thread.title: President Donald Trump to visit Trumbull County next week to sign bill

author: Sabrina Eaton, cleveland.com
title: President Donald Trump to visit Trumbull County next week to sign bill
text: President Donald Trump is expected to sign a bill that reversed an Obama Administration rule intended to keep coal mines from dumping waste into streams.
